    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>Take a look at this similar question.\n<a href=\"https://stackoverflow.com/questions/135971/is-there-a-tool-to-discover-if-the-same-class-exists-in-multiple-jars-in-the-cl#136292\"> Tool to discover same class..</a></p>\n\n<p>I think the most relevant obstacle is if you have a custom classloader ( loading  from a db or ldap ) </p>\n"
