    "question_id" : 227486,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>Edit just 1st line: <code>Main</code>.class</p>\n\n<pre><code>Class&lt;?&gt; c = Main.class;\nString path = c.getResource(c.getSimpleName() + \".class\").getPath().replace(c.getSimpleName() + \".class\", \"\");\n\nSystem.out.println(path);\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>Output: </p>\n\n<pre><code>/C:/Users/Test/bin/\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>Maybe bad style but works fine!</p>\n"
