    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>Typically, we don't what to use hardcoding. We can get className first, and then use ClassLoader to get the class URL.</p>\n\n<pre><code>        String className = MyClass.class.getName().replace(\".\", \"/\")+\".class\";\n        URL classUrl  = MyClass.class.getClassLoader().getResource(className);\n        String fullPath = classUrl==null ? null : classUrl.getPath();\n</code></pre>\n"
