    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>Simple way:</p>\n\n<blockquote>\n  <p>System.out.println(java.lang.String.class.getResource(String.class.getSimpleName()+\".class\"));</p>\n</blockquote>\n\n<p>Out Example:</p>\n\n<blockquote>\n  <p>jar:file:/D:/Java/jdk1.8/jre/lib/rt.jar!/java/lang/String.class</p>\n</blockquote>\n\n<p>Or</p>\n\n<blockquote>\n  <p>String obj = \"simple test\";\n  System.out.println(obj.getClass().getResource(obj.getClass().getSimpleName()+\".class\"));</p>\n</blockquote>\n\n<p>Out Example:</p>\n\n<blockquote>\n  <p>jar:file:/D:/Java/jdk1.8/jre/lib/rt.jar!/java/lang/String.class</p>\n</blockquote>\n"
